    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "Aftermath: After the defeat of Aletheia and the destruction of the red
    sun, the gods are left wondering how to handle souls that would\u2019ve been
    sent to purgatory, and the creatures that still remain in the wastelands of the
    realm.  Without the red sun, purgatory falls into an eternal storm turning it
    into a realm of eternal suffering akin to hell.  This throws off the balance
    of the realms and human souls are unjustly punished with no chance to enter heaven.  "
