    m_Alignment: 1
    m_AlignByGeometry: 0
    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 1
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "First stage of conversion and also lasts the longest, explaining why they
    are numerous in purgatory.  After accepting Aletheia\u2019s offer, the human
    body is twisted and mangled as the jaw is split in half.  Scavengers are the
    fastest and most agile of aletheia\u2019s spawn and possess long scythe-like
    arms used to slash and pierce its prey.  It often takes up to 10 years before
    the next transition starts."
