    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 1
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: 'The Red Sun: The only light looming over the purgatorial realm.  It is
    also a source of immense power capable of creating gateways to neighboring realms. 
    Aletheia has been trying to access its true power to open a portal to the mortal
    realm for centuries but has remained unsuccessful.  Not much else is known about
    its origin as it was never a permanent piece of purgatory.'
